.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD名好好笑<br />\n<br />\n我得閒都會睇<br />\n<br />\n最鐘意佢真係用首詩去連貫離開地球既一刻，好有種寂寥離去，但不失威嚴感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢套戲太撚神，科學、哲學、文學都平衡得好好又發揮得好好，引起到人反思各方面既問題<br />\n由環保開始、到人既存在、老年人心理、親情、人在自然中既無力感<br />\n相對論同量子力學既矛盾、重力既具體面貌...<br />\n<br />\n我既第一次imax都係比左佢，仲要一個人去睇。Murphy同佢講佢地係同年果下，喊撚到癡筋。之後仲要繼續去，反而佢同個女重逢無咁大感動"},{"pid":"2bbe0a21a1e4616b12369472f8a90b5cf4b9f537","tid":110291,"uid":43466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"nolan + hans zimmer = god<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97f046c08bf1f49b93cad09cb6437a8224e8235","tid":110291,"uid":71369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"Interstellar 真係好正，好後悔無係戲院睇，搵日一定要再睇多次"},{"pid":"2c6439c6e5daf16065e7300e652f50e86e64b360","tid":110291,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講真好正，第一次出機場睇imax,  買埋碟黎睇多次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD名好好笑<br />\n<br />\n我得閒都會睇<br />\n<br />\n最鐘意佢真係用首詩去連貫離開地球既一刻，好有種寂寥離去，但不失威嚴感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢套戲太撚神，科學、哲學、文學都平衡得好好又發揮得好好，引起到人反思各方面既問題<br />\n由環保開始、到人既存在、老年人心理、親情、人在自然中既無力感<br />\n相對論同量子力學既矛盾、重力既具體面貌...<br />\n<br />\n我既第一次imax都係比左佢，仲要一個人去睇。Murphy同佢講佢地係同年果下，喊撚到癡筋。之後仲要繼續去，反而佢同個女重逢無咁大感動</blockquote><br />\n第一次blu-ray都比埋佢"},{"pid":"cee5ead6c26a6f48bca43087a1b40c29c4ee9aaf","tid":110291,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"好鍾意佢同個女個段感情<br />\n描寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050e1ab68166e9a585e5d67ebb99b89a9841a468","tid":110291,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Interstellar 真係好正，好後悔無係戲院睇，搵日一定要再睇多次</blockquote><br />\nMe too<br />\n好後悔當時無去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd092cbc02daea5e51f13e251e71e6577969698f","tid":110291,"uid":10331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"2001太空漫遊 <br />\ninterstellar好多野係嚟自呢套"},{"pid":"06c35ce7b4999b3c054dd1bc0e8294861d2e639a","tid":110291,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>太空類既片唔算多<br />\n但都好鍾意睇,星際唯一一套我入戲院睇第2次既戲<br />\n<br />\n另外鍾意關於時空/時間旅行既片</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有咩推介戲？時空旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回到未來當然經典啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另類d既戲 就 慧星來的那一晚(大約依個名(，同異次元駭客"},{"pid":"ea2db959131864ad38bfb2e3614043142c7fbb4e","tid":110291,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"2001<br />\n<br />\nstanley kubrick 好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbca8d936e83caf7f0a50e506bdaeea8ffaa14c","tid":110291,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"仲有 衛斯里 既原子世界都好正"},{"pid":"921f2b37c57c622ddeabc21d2b79af98cd67afa8","tid":110291,"uid":34400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆返去見murphy 個下好感動</blockquote><br />\n個仔冇理過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿仔應該死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ff91e8525fb85b6531ba0806a8cb46c1598c68","tid":110291,"uid":7444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>contact(1997) 幾underrated <br />\n個人認為幾好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢地用同一個科學家顧問，監制，都係Matthew maccortney 做<br />\n我仲寫埋呢2篇影評</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁.<br />\n\r細個睇contact真係好震撼. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e82470eaea4c54e60efc04fbfa3e20485af7945","tid":110291,"uid":736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2001太空漫遊 <br />\ninterstellar好多野係嚟自呢套</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c905f568ac34895102094f2d26446fc408eb0532","tid":110291,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"算係深入淺出硬科幻<br />\n人文方面點到即止<br />\n情節緊湊  老少咸宜<br />\n<br />\n情緒比較千篇一律  <br />\n換句話說都可以叫容易引起共鳴<br />\n<br />\n科幻方面<br />\n普通料  類似橋段係小說俾人用到爛<br />\n視覺表現普普通通<br />\n<br />\n不過咁短時間講到一個完整故事<br />\n有辦法令人坐定定眼都唔眨睇晒<br />\n表達埋環保/探索太空逼切性<br />\n都冇乜人做到"}]}